'''哈頓花園'''（{{lang-en|'''Hatton Garden'''}}），是[[英國|英國]][[倫敦|倫敦]][[卡姆登區|卡姆登區]][[霍本|霍本]]內的一個小區及街道，該處自[[中世紀|中世紀]]已經是倫敦珠寶商的集散地<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.cheap-engagement-rings.co.uk/10-things-you-need-to-know-when-shopping-for-cheap-engagement-rings-online.html|title = 10 things you need to know when shopping for cheap engagement rings online|website = The Cheap Engagement Rings Guide|access-date = 2016-03-06|archive-date = 2020-11-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201125001730/https://www.cheap-engagement-rings.co.uk/10-things-you-need-to-know-when-shopping-for-cheap-engagement-rings-online.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>，亦是[[鑽石|鑽石]]交易的中心，當中最著名的莫過於鑽石商[[戴比爾斯|戴比爾斯]]。近年多間媒體和創意企業亦在此設立辦公室。哈頓花園的地底設有大規模的基礎設施，包括密室、隧道、辦公室和工作坊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/hatton-garden-jewellery-burglary-extraordinary-underworld-of-londons-jewellery-quarter-10169054.html|title=Hatton Garden jewellery burglary: Extraordinary underworld of London’s jewellery quarter|publisher=The Independent|date=10 April 2015|author=Rachel Lichtenstein|accessdate=2016-11-28|archive-date=2019-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402150333/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/hatton-garden-jewellery-burglary-extraordinary-underworld-of-londons-jewellery-quarter-10169054.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，多年來吸引了不少盜竊者前來犯案<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/uk/2015/05/150519_uk_safeboxes_robbery |title=英國哈頓花園珠寶大盜案警方拘捕七人 |publisher=BBC中文網 |date=2015年5月19日}}</ref>。

